OL,4,CBenefit Cosmetics backtracks over NHS
OL,5,Cstaff refusal
OL,6, Benefit Cosmetics has backtracked on a
OL,7, policy that reportedly saw NHS workers
OL,8, turned away for beauty treatments.
OL,10,FA nurse wrote on Facebook that NHS
OL,11,Fstaff were being refused "on the basis
OL,12,Fthat (they) work with Covid patients."
OL,14,FThe beauty brand is now allowing key
OL,15,Fworkers to receive eyebrow and eyelash
OL,16,Ftreatments if they were wearing medical
OL,17,Fgrade PPE when in contact with Covid
OL,18,Fpatients.
OL,20,FA spokeswoman for the firm said it
OL,21,Fregrets "any hurt or upset caused".
